<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-b99b2d7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id="b99b2d7" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="text-editor.default">
<p>We use natural indigo and pumice dyes, offering an environmentally conscious craft experience that celebrates the gifts of nature.</p>
</div>
<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-5dc03d3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image" data-id="5dc03d3" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="image.default"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="attachment-large size-large wp-image-2449" src="../assets/Hands-on-Workshop-Session-1024x683.jpg" sizes="auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="../assets/Hands-on-Workshop-Session-1024x683.jpg 1024w, ../assets/Hands-on-Workshop-Session-300x200.jpg 300w, ../assets/Hands-on-Workshop-Session-768x512.jpg 768w, ../assets/Hands-on-Workshop-Session.jpg 1536w" alt="" width="1024" height="683"></div>
