<li data-start="53" data-end="98">
<p data-start="55" data-end="98">Uses dye based on <strong data-start="73" data-end="98">pumice (grape pomace)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="99" data-end="150">
<p data-start="101" data-end="150"><strong data-start="101" data-end="117">Eco-friendly</strong>, helping reduce industrial waste</p>
</li>
